## 2026-04-03 - No Tokens Studio import format
- Added a dedicated Tokens Studio JSON importer. Added `parseTokensStudioFile`, `isTokensStudioFormat`, and `flattenTsGroup` to `tokenParsers.ts`. Handles both old Tokens Studio format (`value`/`type`) and new format (`$value`/`$type`), respects `$metadata.tokenSetOrder`, skips `$themes`/`$metadata`/`$sets` top-level keys, and maps non-standard type names (e.g. `fontSizes` → `dimension`, `boxShadow` → `shadow`) to DTCG equivalents.
