## 2026-04-03 - BatchEditor handleMove/handleCopy factory + rename unification + skip counter fix
- Extracted `createBatchHandler('move'|'copy')` factory function replacing the two 35-line near-identical `handleMove`/`handleCopy` functions. Factory differences parameterized: API endpoint (`batch-move`/`batch-copy`), response field (`moved`/`copied`), state setter (`setMoving`/`setCopying`), past-tense verb for feedback/undo label.
